# 🇯🇵 **1. JGB MARKET: WHY IT IS UNIQUE**

![Image](https://clientportal.jpx.co.jp/jpxjoinEN/cms/delivery/media/MCFXJJT34RBNFSPJASZKXY2F46XE?utm_source=chatgpt.com)

