# 🔍 **6. PRACTICAL FRAMEWORK TO READ YCC IN REAL TIME**

### **STEP 1 — Track the 10-year yield vs the “reference point”**

If the 10Y > reference + 10bps → pressure rising
If the 10Y > reference + 25bps → market tests BoJ
If the 10Y > reference + 40bps → BoJ must act or reset the regime

### **STEP 2 — Watch BoJ buying operations**

* Size, frequency
* Switching to *fixed-rate operations* → emergency signal
* Reduction in RFI (Rinban) → BoJ comfortable with higher yields

### **STEP 3 — Track supply/demand tensions**

* Auctions tailing more → BoJ stress
* Super-long JGBs (20–40Y) selling off → market expects policy shift
* Futures basis widening → dysfunction

### **STEP 4 — Observe cross-asset signals**

* USDJPY strengthens when yields break ceilings
* YCC tweak speculation priced into JPY vol
* Topix Banks outperform when yields allowed to rise

