# 🇯🇵 **JGB ISSUANCE & ITS RELATION TO RINBAN**

![Image](https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/idXCG_8xT9OM/v2/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png)

